    <titleShort>Avatar</titleShort>
    <slot>Childhood</slot>
    <spawnCategories>
        <li>DivineBackstory</li>
    </spawnCategories>
    <skillGains>
        <li>
            <defName>Social</defName>
            <amount>6</amount>
        </li>
        <li>
            <defName>Intellectual</defName>
            <amount>6</amount>
        </li>
    </skillGains>
    <forcedHediffs>
        <li>Avatar</li>
    </forcedHediffs>
    <forcedTraits>
        <li>
            <defName>GreatMemory</defName>
        </li>
    </forcedTraits>
    <baseDescription>[PAWN_nameDef] is an incarnation of a supreme being, a god walking among mortals. As an avatar of [PAWN_nameDef], this humanoid form only represents a fraction of the power that [PAWN_nameDef] truly possesses. While this form may be hunted or killed by pagans, [PAWN_nameDef] is an eternal being. </baseDescription>
</AlienRace.BackstoryDef>


